# ── OpenClaw workspace leak guard ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# OpenClaw may create identity/metadata files in the workspace root (repo root)
# during agent execution.  These MUST NOT be committed — the canonical copies
# live inside .github-openclaw-intelligence/.  cleanLeakedRootFiles() deletes
# them before `git add`, but .gitignore acts as a final safety net.
# Keep in sync with cleanLeakedRootFiles() in lifecycle/agent.ts and the
# DEFAULT_*_FILENAME constants in openclaw's workspace module.
/AGENTS.md
/BOOTSTRAP.md
/HEARTBEAT.md
/IDENTITY.md
/MEMORY.md
/memory.md
/SOUL
/SOUL.md
/TOOLS.md
/USER.md
/.openclaw/
/memory/
